  "Get In Touch": { fr: "Nous contacter", it: "Contattaci" },
  "Have a question about a perfume, want to suggest a missing bottle, or just want to connect? We'd love to hear from you. Reach out through the email below, and we'll get back to you as soon as we can.": { fr: "Une question sur un parfum, une bouteille √† sugg√©rer ou envie de nous √©crire ? √âcrivez-nous √† l'adresse ci-dessous, nous vous r√©pondrons au plus vite.", it: "Hai una domanda su un profumo, vuoi segnalare un flacone mancante o semplicemente scriverci? Scrivici all'email qui sotto, ti risponderemo al pi√π presto." },
